SUMMARY:FULT — Small Group Call #4
DESCRIPTION:Reach out to your dealer to confirm timing and availability\n\n
 Small group investor call on Thursday\, April 30th.\nIssuer: FULTON FINL C
 ORP (FULT)\n\nDeal context:\nFulton Financial Corporation is conducting fi
 xed income investor calls on April 29-30\, organized by Piper Sandler and 
 J.P. Morgan\, ahead of a potential subordinated notes offering. Subject to
  market conditions\, the holding company plans an SEC-registered offering 
 of subordinated notes with expected ratings of Baa2 (Moody's) and BBB(high
 ) (Morningstar DBRS)\, placing the deal firmly in Investment Grade territo
 ry. No size\, tenor\, or pricing details have been disclosed at this manda
 te stage\, with Piper Sandler coordinating logistics for the investor call
 s.
